vikunja-description =
    Vikunja is a self-hosted, open-source project management and to-do application.

    It covers everything from simple personal task lists to full team project management
    with kanban boards, Gantt charts, due dates, reminders, file attachments, and labels.
    Multiple projects can be organized into namespaces. Users sign in via Kanidm OIDC
    and can collaborate on shared projects and tasks.

vikunja-features =
    - Tasks with sub-tasks, due dates, priorities, and reminders
    - Kanban board view
    - Gantt chart view
    - Team collaboration with shared projects
    - File attachments and comments on tasks
    - Labels and filters
    - OIDC single sign-on via Kanidm
    - REST API for integrations
    - Optional PostgreSQL backend
